<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-70-0499 </DOCNO><TEXT>The complex conditions of nonactive pre-complex tests of technologicalsystems at the 1st unit of the V-2 nuclear power plant are analysed,including the final stages of assembly work. Also described is the organizationof work carried out within the pre-complex tests of auxiliary systemsof the 2nd unit of the V-2 nuclear power plant. Examples are given ofinteresting technical ideas for the tests of replenishment of the primarycoolant circuit. The schedule of the testing is documented and a comparisonmade of testing the 1st and 2nd units. (B.S.). 1 tab.</TEXT></DOC>